Package it.polito.dp2.RNS

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionReader
    An interface for reading information about a connection in the RNS system.
    GateReader
    An interface for reading information about a gate in the RNS system.
    IdentifiedEntityReader
    An interface for accessing the main information associated to a generic entity.
    ParkingAreaReader
    An interface for reading information about a parking area in the RNS system.
    PlaceReader
    An interface for reading information about a place in the RNS system.
    RnsReader
    An interface for reading information about the RNS system.
    RoadSegmentReader
    An interface for reading information about a road segment in the RNS system.
    VehicleReader
    An interface for reading information about a vehicle in the RNS system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RnsReaderFactory
    Defines a factory API that enables applications to obtain one or more objects implementing the RnsReader interface.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GateType
    GateType represents the type of a gate in the RNS system.
    VehicleState
    VehicleState represents the state of a vehicle that is in a place in the RNS system
    VehicleType
    VeghicleType represents the type of a vehicle that can be tracked in the RNS system The type can be one of the following: CAR, TRUCK, SHUTTLE, CARAVAN
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RnsReaderException
    An exception thrown if an implementation of RnsReader cannot be created.
  • Error Summary 
    Error Description
    FactoryConfigurationError
    Thrown if the implementation of the concrete factory is not available or cannot be instantiated.
